      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! We're excited to offer this vehicle as an affordable entry point for someone who loves a hands-on challenge. While it needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic opportunity to bring a car back to life at a great value. If you're looking for a budget-friendly project with plenty of potential, this is the one for you!",
