    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable, budget-friendly commuter. While the car runs and drives well, the exterior shows clear signs of age, including several noticeable scratches on the passenger side doors and a small dent on the rear fender. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few minor stains from regular use. It has been serviced regularly, but buyers should expect some upcoming minor maintenance items typical for a car of this age and mileage.",
